<p><strong>No Bake Energy Balls</strong>. Loaded with old fashioned oats, peanut butter and flax seeds. These Energy Balls are a healthy protein packed breakfast or snack!</p>



<p>Looking for more energy bite recipes? Try my <a href="https://chefsavvy.com/almond-joy-energy-bites/">Almond Joy Protein Balls</a> or <a href="https://chefsavvy.com/chocolate-peanut-butter-energy-bites/">Chocolate Peanut Butter Energy Bites</a>!</p>



